    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><rs key="#Offersio/donatio">Donatio</rs> omnium bonorum pertinentium ad
                                <persName><name ref="Ungarus">Hungarum</name></persName> filium
                        quondam <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Dominicus"
                            >Dominici</name></persName> <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs> tam in 
                        <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs> quam in planis, tam
                        in <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> quam extra, tam mobilium quam immobilium, facta ab eodem favore
                        domini <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1599">Hyeronimi</persName> 
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> <orgName key="#Offersio/donatio #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName key="#Offersio/donatio #Monasteries" ref="#places/4179">Pomposiani</placeName></orgName> 
                        in nomine sui <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>. Actum in 
                        <rs key="#Burgi">burgo</rs>
                        civitatis <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/7">Bononię</placeName>, in curte ante <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>. 
                        Subscriptum ab Hungaro et duobus
                        filiis eius et aliis. 1081, 25 ianuarii, indictione IV.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Mezzetti, <foreign>Le carte</foreign>, vol. 2, doc. 86 (in preparazione).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mezzetti, per la sua edizione delle carte di Pomposa, si rifà in parte a una
                    serie di regesti realizzati da Arcari nel XVIII secolo (Arcari,
                        <foreign>Index</foreign>, II (a. 1741), c. 128).</p>
            </div>
